    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Magical reagents slosh inside this rime\u2011frosted pottery jar the size of a human head. Despite appearing to be rimed in hoarfrost, the jar is warm to the touch. Ilverani wizards create *rime jars* to sustain themselves during the coldest winter nights.",
